1. To install follow these instructions - http://maven.apache.org/guides/getting-started/maven-in-five-minutes.html
2. Github - www.github.com/shanedownfall/CNGLSummarizer
3. For usage examples check the classes under main in the summarizer package.
4. To browse the docs open docs/index.html in any browser.
5. I have yet to document the configuration file, it should be fairly self explanatory, but I'll explain it all next week.